954183047443"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In problem 7, I tried for the easiest proof involving limits that I could \
come up with. The ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"\[Delta]", "'"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "cb2f2825-e16b-484d-b225-f17994650401"],
 " that worked in the second limit was 2\[Delta].\n\nA slightly harder \
version of Problem 7 would be to show that the following two limits (if one \
exists), must be equal, and find the \[Delta] that makes it so.\n\nSo, assume \
this exists:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8284474725875397`*^9, 3.828447589824294*^9}, {
  3.828447670769052*^9, 3.82844769501711*^9}, {3.828447786409136*^9, 
